Install grafana on Mac:
===========================

1) download the tar

curl -O https://dl.grafana.com/oss/release/grafana-8.0.3.darwin-amd64.tar.gz

2) extract the tar

3) go to bin directory & execute the  below cmd

./grafana-server web

4) open browser and go to
  http://localhost:3000

  default username : admin
  default password : admin



